nbsp;&nbsp;0.87%&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Depozitář historických vozidel&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;25&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;0.84%&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Kovárna v Těšanech&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;25&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;0.84%&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Kryt Denis&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;25&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;0.84%&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Památník Leoše Janáčka&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;25&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;0.84%&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Stará huť u Adamova&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;25&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;0.84%&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary>ZOO (Zoos) — 772 návštěvníků (0.18% of Total Demand)</summary>\n\n<table style=\"width: auto\">\n<tr><th align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Name&nbsp;&nbsp;</th><th align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Modeled Demand&nbsp;&nbsp;</th><th align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;% of ZOO Demand&nbsp;&nbsp;</th></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Zoo Brno&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;740&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;95.85%&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Exotická zahrada Přibice&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;32&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;4.15%&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary>Přírodní zajímavosti (Natural Features) — 53 návštěvníků (0.01% of Total Demand)</summary>\n\n<table style=\"width: auto\">\n<tr><th align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Name&nbsp;&nbsp;</th><th align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Modeled Demand&nbsp;&nbsp;</th><th align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;% of Přírodní zajímavosti Demand&nbsp;&nbsp;</th></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Jeskyně Výpustek&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;53&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;100.00%&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary>Sakrální památky (Religious Sites) — 214 návštěvníků (0.05% of Total Demand)</summary>\n\n<table style=\"width: auto\">\n<tr><th align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Name&nbsp;&nbsp;</th><th align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Modeled Demand&nbsp;&nbsp;</th><th align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;% of Sakrální památky Demand&nbsp;&nbsp;</th></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Klášter Rosa coeli&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;137&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;64.02%&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Kapucínská hrobka&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;60&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;28.04%&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Synagoga Dolní Kounice&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;17&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;7.94%&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary>Zábavní parky a aquaparky (Theme Parks & Aquaparks) — 1,001 návštěvníků (0.23% of Total Demand)</summary>\n\n<table style=\"width: auto\">\n<tr><th align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Name&nbsp;&nbsp;</th><th align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Modeled Demand&nbsp;&nbsp;</th><th align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;% of Zábavní parky a aquaparky Demand&nbsp;&nbsp;</th></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Wellness Kuřim&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;510&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;50.95%&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;DinoPark Vyškov&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;369&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;36.86%&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Permonium&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;122&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;12.19%&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n</details>\n\n### Sport\n\n<details>\n<summary>Fotbalové stadiony (Football Stadiums) — 230 diváků (0.05% of Total Demand)</summary>\n\n<table style=\"width: auto\">\n<tr><th align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Name&nbsp;&nbsp;</th><th align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Modeled Demand&nbsp;&nbsp;</th><th align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;% of Fotbalové stadiony Demand&nbsp;&nbsp;</th></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Stadion Srbská — FC Zbrojovka Brno&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;127&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;55.22%&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Sportovní areál Drnovice — MFK Vyškov&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;53&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;23.04%&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Stadion SK Líšeň — SK Líšeň&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;50&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;21.74%&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary>Ledové arény (Ice Hockey Arenas) — 516 diváků (0.12% of Total Demand)</summary>\n\n<table style=\"width: auto\">\n<tr><th align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Name&nbsp;&nbsp;</th><th align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Modeled Demand&nbsp;&nbsp;</th><th align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;% of Ledové arény Demand&nbsp;&nbsp;</th></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Winning Group Arena — HC Kometa Brno&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;516&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;100.00%&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n</details>\n\n## Additional Features\n\n- **Building Collision** — A buildings index is included for all non-filtered buildings, assigning each a flat foundation depth of **−10 m** in-game. This provides underground collision geometry so that tunnels interact correctly with building footprints.\n\n- **Neighborhood Labels** — Three layers of place name labels are embedded in the map:\n  - _City labels_ — Major city names at the metropolitan scale.\n  - _Municipality labels_ — Names of all obce within the map boundary.\n  - _Neighborhood labels_ — Basic settlement unit names (ZSJ — _základní sídelní jednotka_) from RUIAN cadastral data.\n\n## Methodology\n\nThis map is generated through a six-phase pipeline that transforms Czech government census and employment statistics into georeferenced origin/destination demand points.\n\n**Point Seeding:** Candidate points are placed within each _obec_ (municipality) using population-weighted centroids derived from GHS-POP 100 m population grid data (JRC Global Human Settlement Layer R2023A).\n\n**Mesh Reconciliation:** Initial point populations are refined by solving a constrained convex optimization that approximates each point's mass to residential and economic mesh ideals while preserving CZSO 2021 Census (Sčítání lidu, domů a bytů 2021) totals for each obec.\n\n**Aggregation:** A global scaling factor reconciles the mismatch between boundary-captured employed residents (from Sčítání 2021) and workplace employees (from CZSO employment statistics).\n\n**Commute Assignment:** Commute flows are assigned directly from _DojizdkovyProud_ — the official 2021 Census O/D commuter flow table at _ZSJ-díl_ (sub-municipal) granularity.\n\n**Special Demand Injection:** Non-commuter demand generators — airports, universities, major sports facilities, libraries, and tourism attractions — are injected as an additive layer. Airport demand from Czech CAA (ÚCL) statistics; university demand from MŠMT DSIA F21 faculty enrollment; attraction demand from tourdata.cz visitor counts across all 14 Czech kraje (~1,800 attractions). Sports arena demand derived from per-club average attendance × home matches; library demand from per-library _návštěvníci_ counts in operator výroční zprávy and NIPOS aggregates.\n\n**Layout Reconciliation:** A final spatial pass resolves point overlaps and ensures map clickability while keeping special-demand locations fixed.\n\n## Data Sources\n\nAll demand modeling is derived from freely available Czech government statistical datasets and public geospatial resources.\n\n- **2021 Census** (Sčítání lidu, domů a bytů 2021 / SLDB 2021) — [ČSÚ / CZSO](https://www.czso.cz/)\n- **Commute O/D at ZSJ-díl level** (DojizdkovyProud) — [ČSÚ / CZSO](https://www.czso.cz/)\n- **Workplace Employment Statistics** (Počet obsazených pracovních míst) — [ČSÚ Geodata](https://geodata.statistika.cz/)\n- **100 m Population Grid** (GHS-POP R2023A) — [JRC / EU Copernicus](https://ghsl.jrc.ec.europa.eu/)\n- **Cadastral Boundaries** (RUIAN — Registr územní identifikace, adres a nemovitostí) — [ČÚZK](https://www.cuzk.cz/)\n- **Faculty Enrollment Data** (MŠMT DSIA F21) — [MŠMT](https://dsia.msmt.cz/)\n- **Airport Passenger Statistics** — [ÚCL / Czech CAA](https://www.caa.cz/statistiky)\n- **Tourism Visitor Statistics** — [tourdata.cz / CzechTourism](https://tourdata.cz/)\n- **Library Visitor Statistics** — [NIPOS Statistika kultury](https://www.statistikakultury.cz/) + per-library výroční zprávy\n- **Football League Attendance** (Chance Liga + Chance národní liga) — [chanceliga.cz](https://www.chanceliga.cz/statistiky-rekordy)\n- **Ice Hockey League Attendance** (Tipsport Extraliga + Chance Liga) — [hokej.cz](https://www.hokej.cz/)\n- **Overture Maps Foundation** — [Overture](https://overturemaps.org/)\n\n## License\n\nThis map data is released under the [GNU General Public License v3.0](https://github.com/ahkimn/subwaybuilder-eu-maps/blob/main/LICENSE).\n\n## Credits\n\nMap authored by [Yukina-](https://subwaybuildermodded.com/credits/)",
